{"tw": {"2197740": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "哥布林地下城", "steam_appid": 2197740, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "controller_support": "full", "dlc": [4065570, 4259400, 4080560, 4075410, 4075480, 4075580, 4075350, 4064970, 4065240, 4268020], "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197740/extras/a18617ae8c2e0192fa0eedbf0c8a5972.poster.avif?t=1775736016\" width=850 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197740/extras/a18617ae8c2e0192fa0eedbf0c8a5972.webm?t=1775736016\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197740/extras/a18617ae8c2e0192fa0eedbf0c8a5972.mp4?t=1775736016\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>埃羅提斯已淪陷</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成群的地精焚毀城市、摧毀文明，並奴役倖存者。最後的希望，是精靈女祭司的古老儀式——她們從異界召喚了一位女英雄。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197740/extras/4043d39fbb47d39f7cae84ac1141c5be.poster.avif?t=1775736016\" width=850 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197740/extras/4043d39fbb47d39f7cae84ac1141c5be.webm?t=1775736016\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197740/extras/4043d39fbb47d39f7cae84ac1141c5be.mp4?t=1775736016\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>異世界</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是艾莉，在我們的世界中喪生，卻被上古神祇復活的年輕女性。為了回到故鄉，你必須殺出地精重圍、精通魔法，並向地精之王發起挑戰。每一次死亡都不是終點，而是邁向更強大的階段。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197740/extras/a3ff752bc079aa07a745cd78a9b58d39.poster.avif?t=1775736016\" width=850 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197740/extras/a3ff752bc079aa07a745cd78a9b58d39.webm?t=1775736016\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197740/extras/a3ff752bc079aa07a745cd78a9b58d39.mp4?t=1775736016\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>遊戲特色：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >40 種獨特敵人與 170 種變體——從小兵到扭曲的怪物</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 名具獨特機制的頭目，需要審慎的策略</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 大魔法學派與 60+ 法術——自由組合致命連招</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >裝備與技能成長，魔法養成</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100+ 隨機事件與火辣邂逅，改變每一次旅程</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >300 張含露骨插畫的收藏卡</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 個氛圍各異的場景，各自暗藏危機</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >12 個獨特成人場景——可互動、可升級，並支援 X-Ray 透視</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197740/extras/9211283fb60f682403e13cca5cd20e15.poster.avif?t=1775736016\" width=850 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197740/extras/9211283fb60f682403e13cca5cd20e15.webm?t=1775736016\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197740/extras/9211283fb60f682403e13cca5cd20e15.mp4?t=1775736016\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>死亡是旅程的一部分</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次失敗都會讓你更強。再度復甦、適應局勢、強化能力並解鎖新法術，一步步殺到地精之王面前。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class