043d39fbb47d39f7cae84ac1141c5be.webm?t=1775736016\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197740/extras/4043d39fbb47d39f7cae84ac1141c5be.mp4?t=1775736016\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Another World</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are Eli, a young woman who died in our world and was resurrected by an ancient deity. To return home, you must cut through goblin armies, master magic, and challenge the Goblin King himself. Each death isn’t the end — it’s a step toward greater power.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197740/extras/a3ff752bc079aa07a745cd78a9b58d39.poster.avif?t=1775736016\" width=850 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197740/extras/a3ff752bc079aa07a745cd78a9b58d39.webm?t=1775736016\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197740/extras/a3ff752bc079aa07a745cd78a9b58d39.mp4?t=1775736016\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >40 unique enemies and 170 variants — from lesser beasts to twisted abominations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 bosses with unique mechanics that demand real strategy</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 schools of magic and 60+ spells — build lethal combinations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Progression of gear and skills, magic development</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100+ random events and spicy encounters that change your run</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >300 collectible cards with explicit illustrations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" 